column5: i bought a digi cam so i will be taking lots of pics and i'll post them on mon cheers and good fishin to all
thanks look forward to seeing some pics ..hope your weekend is successful!
hitting the ganny on opener combat fishing at it's finest good luck
wait, this might be more like it...

We will also be in the combat zone on the Ganny may see you out there! And no I was not in that one.  FLEX
